1/ HOW TO COMPILE THE PROJECT
To compile the project, you have to use the "make" command.
Just type "make" when you are in the root directory of the project.

2/ HOW TO USE THE PROJECT
Execution : ./main <mode>

Mode : 1 displays the graphical user interface
       2 executes adaboost on set of 5 images and select 3 WeakClassifiers.
       Their index, threshold,etc... are then written in the file 
       ADATEST.
       3 displays the integral image of a selected picture and write
         the Haarfeatures of this picture in HAARCARACS.
       
After that, you can use the "make clean" command to remove all
the files resulting from the compilation.
